{"word":"G419 - ἀνεξερεύνητος - anexereúnētos - an-ex-er-yoo'-nay-tos - Unsearchable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνεξερεύνητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anexereúnētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ex-er-yoo'-nay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unsearchable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆராயப்படாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"that cannot be searched out"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G1830 - ἐξερευνάω - exereunáō - ex-er-yoo-nah'-o/1830\">G1830</a>; <i>not searched out</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>inscrutable:</i> - unsearchable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}